    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Current function reads:</p>

<p>public function inheritsRole($role, $inherit, $onlyParents = false)
{
    return $this-&gt;_getRoleRegistry()-&gt;inherits($role, $inherit, $onlyParents = false);
}</p>

<p>This results in the $onlyParents parameter always being set to false, instead of passing the actual value on towards the private function. Remove the = false from the function call.</p>

